"""Homing routine."""
with expected_protocol(ik.thorlabs.APTMotorController, [init_kdc101[0],
    ThorLabsPacket(message_id=ThorLabsCommands.MOT_MOVE_HOME, param1=1,
    param2=0, dest=80, source=1, data=None).pack()], [init_kdc101[1],
    ThorLabsPacket(message_id=ThorLabsCommands.MOT_MOVE_HOMED, param1=1,
    param2=0, dest=80, source=1, data=None).pack()], sep='') as apt:
    apt.channel[0].go_home()
